## Interface: 120005,120007
## Title: Cairn
## Notes: A modern alternative to Ace3 for WoW addon authors. Composable libraries (Addon, DB, Slash, Events, Locale, Log, Util, Hooks, Timer, Settings, Callback, Media, Gui) with a flagship Settings library that bridges to Blizzard's native Settings panel.
## Author: ChronicTinkerer
## Version: 1
## SavedVariables: CairnDB
## LoadOnDemand: 0
## X-Curse-Project-ID: 1532175
## X-Wago-ID: b6XemBKp
## X-WoWI-ID: 27134
## X-License: MIT

# ----- Vendored LibStub (only loaded when Cairn runs as a standalone
#       addon for development/testing; in production the consumer addon
#       supplies its own LibStub via embeds and this is a no-op since
#       LibStub is idempotent)
embeds\LibStub\LibStub.lua

# ----- Libraries load here as they ship.
CairnAddon\Cairn-Addon.lua
CairnDB\Cairn-DB.lua
CairnEvents\Cairn-Events.lua
CairnSlash\Cairn-Slash.lua
CairnLocale\Cairn-Locale.lua
CairnLog\Cairn-Log.lua
CairnHooks\Cairn-Hooks.lua
CairnTimer\Cairn-Timer.lua
CairnCallback\Cairn-Callback.lua
